Title: Holy Cornholio
Plot: Butt-Head is really screwed when a visit to the hospital once again awakens The Great Cornoholio in Beavis. But two rooms over, the leader of a cult has died. Is the Great Cornholio destined to be the cult's idiot savior? Cornholio's hopped up babble certainly sounds holy, and the idiot worship begins. Soon they're promised to be with their pick of the ladies. Will they mess this one up? You bet your bunghole!
